<i>Fu Manchu</i> you're starting there.

105
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:07,195
Man of my dreams.

106
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:10,909
- Sorry, l can't take them anywhere.
- lt's all right.

107
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:13,640
Four beers for the lynch mob.

108
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:18,635
Sorry. l didn't mean to ruin
your wonderful surprise there.

109
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,518
Don't go away.

110
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:24,070
Casanova, any new letters
