you can tell us what this is about.

119
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:04,913
l am glad you're sitting down because
you are not going to believe this.

120
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,275
l didn't believe it myself.

121
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:12,310
l've found Dimeglio.

122
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:19,598
- Our principal from St. Clete's?
- l heard she passed away.

123
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:23,398
Hell wouldn't take her.

124
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:30,193
She comes in every night at seven, sits
at this table and has a gin and grapefruit.

125
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:34,516
- And she will be here again tonight.
- So what?

126
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,516
So what?

127
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:41,389
This is our chance to pay her back
for all those things she did to us.

128
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:45,473
Carla, that was 20 years ago.
We were just girls.

129
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:49,076
But we took an oath that we'd get her.
Don't you remember?

130
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,631
She's coming. Get behind the bar.

131
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:54,837
- Carla, come on.
- Get behind the bar.

132
00:10:55,000 --> 00:11:00,916
Don't worry. All the hate's going to come
back as soon as you look at her.

133
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:03,913
- Hey, ladies.
- Get down.

134
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,632
- Hi.
- Hello.

135
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:11,598
Would you take this table?
That one's taken.

136
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:16,875
- What are you going to have?
- Gin and grapefruit juice.

137
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:19,600
- One gin and grapefruit.
- Coming up.

138
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:27,754
He liked your order
and l'm going to get it.

139
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,516
What do you think?

140
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:40,236
