lt's been a long time,
but l don't think it's her either.

145
00:11:57,000 --> 00:12:00,515
- So what if it is? Who cares?
- Get down! l care.

146
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:03,956
lf you don't want to help me,
l'll get her without you.

147
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:07,237
- Fine. 'Cause l don't want any part of it.
- Desert me.

148
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:10,756
Just stay there
because l don't want her to see you.

149
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:15,198
- What are we supposed to do here?
- Find some way of amusing yourselves.

150
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,792
OK.

151
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:34,838
Carla's been moping around 'cause none
of her chums will back her up on this.

152
